@DigiMerchantBE_HostAddress = http://localhost:5141

### Login (seed user: admin / Admin@123)
POST {{DigiMerchantBE_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

###

### Current user (paste accessToken from login)
GET {{DigiMerchantBE_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Roles for register dropdown (no SUPER_ADMIN, from DB)
GET {{DigiMerchantBE_HostAddress}}/api/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Register user (requires USER_MANAGEMENT)
POST {{DigiMerchantBE_HostAddress}}/api/users/register
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "operator01",
  "password": "Operator@123",
  "fullName": "Operator One",
  "email": "operator01@example.com",
  "phone": "0901234567",
  "roleCode": "OPERATOR"
}

###
